node.text:
A bit of my Push + Pull day today:

Incline Chest Press 
5x5
Bent Over T-Bar Row
5x5
Seated Close Grip Rows
4x 12-15
Neutral Grip Dumbbell Chest Press 
4x12-15
•
•
•
If I’m being 100% honest, it should have been a rest day because I was feeling very fatigued. As a result, my performance suffered more than I would have liked.

Never underestimate the importance of recovery! Getting good quality sleep, drinking enough water, fuelling your body well, stretching and foam rolling will all aid you in recovering from your workout - and better prepare you for your next session. Train hard, but don’t forget to rest well! 😴 
•
•
•
